To compile/run one of the GEANT4 examples then do the following (this is for the B1 example).

cd /work/`whoami`/STMDAQ-TestBeam//geant
source setup.sh
cp -R  $G4INSTALL/examples/basic/B1 .
mkdir B1Build
cd B1Build
cmake3  -DGeant4_DIR=$G4DIR/Geant4-10.7.3 ../B1
make
./B1Example

There are issues with OpenGL forwarding over X11 to a mac though. 
On the mac this command helps but doesn't completely fix the problem ie a window pops up but 
then immediately disappears as oppsoed to never appearing at all...

defaults write org.macosforge.xquartz.X11 enable_iglx -bool true

